{"tid":1718152,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"坦白講，如果真係行動升級既話，裝修嘅標準都要進一步。","createTime":"2019-11-13T19:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T02:02:46.000Z","uid":34676,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a16fe9b8cd4052c88f2915901f8315edfa0f34f5","tid":1718152,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:00:30.000Z","msg":"真係頂唔順有啲人屌人亂裝修<br />\n都已經過咗成個月<br />\n口頭上就口口聲聲話要升級，但就永遠俾個「黑裝修藍罷xxxx」困死自己。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，所有撐警/奶共/中資 一律裝修啦，仲咁撚得閒罷罷罷，你估香港人真係咁有骨氣罷買到咩，好似罷工咁，根本有堆人骨子裡就犯賤係都要偷偷地買/偷偷地返工。<br />\n<br />\n如果行動升級，但裝修指標唔改變嘅話，咁叫咩升級？"},{"pid":"c2996c80f78eeaae867576d08d5ddf9415d9ea9b","tid":1718152,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:00:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c6dc8d3114e39a98e09ec7044bc3383e378c5e9","tid":1718152,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:03:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f9550ccb45e6ed6b8fb5dd19493297b8f7f7639","tid":1718152,"uid":297672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:05:26.000Z","msg":"利申，我係認同，咁會多啲人被罷工，社會停擺。但相信好多人會話我哋成為咗林鄭口中嘅暴徒/ 失民意。<br />\n<br />\n民意係重要嘅，所以點樣去解釋，帶返落政府就好關鍵。政府唔應該再逃避五大訴求，再逃避只會影響民生，令社會癱瘓。"},{"pid":"d7b9306960e940dca1b9e1178e1326ad08d6ffa2","tid":1718152,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T23:44:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n借位，請幫推文宣方向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1718126\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1718126</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799b35b3ec621349915987adc72c200f67032d78","tid":1718152,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T23:48:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">繼續啊繼續啊繼續啊繼續到落實五大訴求煲底相見，唔可以比手足既血白流啊屌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民同我早早早早早起，繼續無限三罷，癱瘓交通，攬炒經濟！</span><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人已經退無可退！Neve forgive. Never forget. </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VsHV0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VsHV0b.jpg&h=53f43c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cdzLMW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cdzLMW.jpg&h=f251c786&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1faa72c57424f29e571ec20c3267331af1cc573a","tid":1718152,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T23:48:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f5f21cd25b1d2fbb7cda5d6d461e8ee304779ff","tid":1718152,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited